        "highlightWords": ["v-athina-001", "v-xenodocheio-001"],
        "speakerNote": "Alex reflects on everything he learned today"
      },
      {
        "greek": "Σήμερα έμαθε πολλά: ναι, όχι, γεια σου, ευχαριστώ, παρακαλώ, καλημέρα, καλησπέρα, καληνύχτα.",
        "english": "Today he learned a lot: yes, no, hello, thank you, please, good morning, good evening, good night.",
        "swedish": "Idag lärde han sig mycket: ja, nej, hej, tack, varsågod, god morgon, god kväll, god natt.",
        "highlightWords": [],
        "speakerNote": "A summary of all the words from Chapter 1"
      },
      {
        "greek": "Η ρεσεψιονίστ λέει: «Καληνύχτα!» Ο Αλεξ απαντάει: «Καληνύχτα! Ευχαριστώ!»",
        "english": "The receptionist says: \"Good night!\" Alex replies: \"Good night! Thank you!\"",
        "swedish": "Receptionisten säger: \"God natt!\" Alex svarar: \"God natt! Tack!\"",
        "highlightWords": ["v-kalinychta-001", "v-efcharisto-001"],
        "speakerNote": "Alex uses his Greek naturally for the first time"
      }
    ],
    "comprehensionQuestions": [
